---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Canopy">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-[#00D4FF]">About Canopy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg">
      <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-6">
        Canopy is building the future of agriculture technology. We believe that data-driven 
        insights and modern tools can help growers of all sizes optimize their operations 
        and build more sustainable, profitable businesses.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#00D4FF]">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 mb-4">
        To empower horticulture growers with accessible technology that increases yields, 
        reduces waste, and creates a more resilient food system.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#00D4FF]">What We Do</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/70">
        <li>Provide data analytics tools tailored for horticulture operations</li>
        <li>Connect growers with industry benchmarks and best practices</li>
        <li>Build a community of forward-thinking agriculture professionals</li>
        <li>Develop integrations with existing farm management systems</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#00D4FF]">Get in Touch</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70">
        Interested in learning more? Reach out to us at <a href="mailto:hello@canopy.ag" class="text-[#00D4FF]">hello@canopy.ag</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>